SQL_STMT_U.val: select DCDD.DCDD_ADMNO, DCDD.DCDD_CLNTNO, DCDD.DCDD_DEBC, DCDD.DCDD_HADR_NAME1, DCDD.DCDD_HADR_CITY, DCDD.DCDD_REFERENCENUMBER from :1/DCDD DCDD where DCDD.DCDD_ADMNO = :2 and DCDD.DCDD_CLNTNO = :3 and not ( exists (select * from :1/DEBC DEBC where DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO = DCDD.DCDD_ADMNO and DEBC.DEBC_CLNTNO = DCDD.DCDD_CLNTNO and DEBC.DEBC_DEBC = DCDD.DCDD_DEBC and DEBC.DEBC_DATDELETED is null)) for fetch only
